data.name: Research: A Dose of AI for Disease Prevention and Treatment
description:
⚡ Modified an existing U-Net (Convolutional Neural Network) implementation to perform blood vessel segmentation on a new database of ROP images from the Children’s Hospital of Pennsylvania | Python, TensorFlow, Sklearn 
 ⚡ Incorporated multi-view eye imagery and different classifiers to compare and improve sensitivity and specificity metrics
